00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:30.699
la coruña el próximo

00:00:30.699 --> 00:00:31.879
31 de marzo.

00:00:32.619 --> 00:00:34.579
Por otro lado, RTO

00:00:34.579 --> 00:00:35.560
ve informa que el

00:00:35.560 --> 00:00:37.079
FC Barcelona ha consolidado

00:00:37.079 --> 00:00:38.020
su ventaja en su

00:00:38.020 --> 00:00:39.020
