00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:39.179
de,

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:40.659
campeones frente al Real

00:00:40.659 --> 00:00:42.079
Madrid, tras haber marcado

00:00:42.079 --> 00:00:42.780
